{"type":"text","timestamp":1782363108465,"sessionID":"ses_102e4b379ffemg20qTMGqq4dM7","part":{"id":"prt_efd1e92c10019H7OdE6ZX8osQp","messageID":"msg_efd1e7111001opdBTdMCtfAOjL","sessionID":"ses_102e4b379ffemg20qTMGqq4dM7","type":"text","text":"Covered this bounded repair by updating the authority coverage records for the architecture-risk group so its broad whole-file endpoints now point to concrete config keys, resource names, and startup profile entries. No target app code changes were needed.\n\n**Covered Entries**\n- `app-build-gradle-kts-52a26dc1e9-003-android-platform-component-lifecycle-suc`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with `entry/cjpm.toml::name`, `entry/cjpm.toml::profile.build.combined.ohos_app_cangjie_entry`, `AppScope/app.json5::bundleName`, `entry/src/main/module.json5::srcEntry`, `entry/src/main/module.json5::mainElement`.\n- `build-gradle-kts-6cd8a326ab-002-android-platform-component-lifecycle-suc`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with `build-profile.json5::modules`, `build-profile.json5::products`, `hvigorfile.ts::appTasks`, plus precise `entry/cjpm.toml` keys.\n- `app-src-main-androidmanifest-xml-e5fadea668-001-android-resource-configuration-must-be-m`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with specific `AppScope/app.json5` and `entry/src/main/module.json5` fields plus `entry/src/main/resources/base/element/color.json::start_window_background`.\n- `app-src-main-androidmanifest-xml-525ca85433-002-intent-uri-bundle-deeplink-or-cross-scre`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with `entry/src/main/module.json5::exported`, `::skills`, `::mainElement`, and `entry/src/main/resources/base/profile/main_pages.json::pages/FoodikeBootstrap`.\n- `app-src-main-res-values-themes-xml-1c5ca98798-001-android-resource-configuration-must-be-m`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with `entry/src/main/module.json5::startWindowBackground`, `::startWindowIcon`, `entry/src/main/resources/base/element/color.json::start_window_background`, and the icon asset files.\n- `app-src-main-res-values-themes-xml-b98f18ad24-003-android-android-values-file-should-be-ma`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with `entry/src/main/module.json5::startWindowBackground`, `::pages`, `entry/src/main/resources/base/element/color.json::start_window_background`, and `main_pages.json::pages/FoodikeBootstrap`.\n- `app-src-main-res-values-colors-xml-8e1c28dae7-001-android-resource-configuration-must-be-m`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with concrete color names `white`, `black`, `LightGreen`, `DarkGreen` in both entry/AppScope color catalogs plus `module.json5::startWindowBackground`.\n- `app-src-main-res-values-colors-xml-8d1c4a6521-002-android-android-values-file-should-be-ma`\n  Replaced broad endpoints with concrete reusable color-name endpoints in both color catalogs, including `start_window_background`.\n\n**Remaining Entries**\n- For this bounded group, the touched broad-endpoint debt is repaired in `source-coverage-matrix.json`.\n- Final group verdict is still pending workflow recomputation of `phase-group-verdicts`.\n- Other current-phase partial groups still exist, but they are outside this bounded repair unless the runner reclassifies them after recompute.\n- The known current-phase functional debt around `implemented-simplified` startup/navigation rows remains out of scope for this prompt because this session was limited to the `architecture-risk-broad-target-endpoints` group.\n\n**Source Paths / Clusters Handled**\n- `app/build.gradle.kts`\n- `build.gradle.kts`\n- `app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml`\n- `app/src/main/res/values/themes.xml`\n- `app/src/main/res/values/colors.xml`\n\n**Out Of Scope Warnings**\n- I did not repair other phase-01 partial groups such as `source-behavior-app`, `source-behavior-kotlin-source`, `resource-migration-manifest`, `resource-migration-res-values`, or verification debt beyond the endpoint precision needed here.\n- I did not implement future-phase behavior or alter platform capability rows because this group had no capability rows and the target behavior already